    @Mojo(name="generate",
      defaultPhase=GENERATE_SOURCES)
public class AerialMavenGeneratorPlugin
extends org.apache.maven.plugin.AbstractMojo
    Generates Cucumber feature files based on Aerial document descriptions. Input documents can be stored in many accessible types (controlled by inputType field.
